OL,9,G0800 Bargain-Loving Brits in the Sun
OL,10,     FWe meet Ellie and Jim who have
OL,11,     Fjust got married and also set up
OL,12,     Ftheir brand-new cafe in Benidorm.
OL,13,G0900 Bargain-Loving Brits in the Sun
OL,14,     FWe meet climbing hostel owners Sam
OL,15,     Fand Rich. They have a coach-load
OL,16,     Fof guests about to arrive, giving
OL,17,     Fthem a "mountain to climb" to get
OL,18,     Feverything ready in time.
