OL,8,     Fbroke into their house and changed
OL,9,     Fthe locks. Paul learned that his
OL,10,     Ffather's tenant owed 20k in rent.
OL,11,G1100 Traffic Cops
OL,12,     FDrink drivers are increasingly
OL,13,     Ftrying to come up with ways to
OL,14,     Fbeat the system. One driver claims
OL,15,     Fto have had a single swig of beer,
OL,16,     Fforcing the cops to wait 20
OL,17,     Fminutes.
