OL,5,G2000 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,6,     FIt's a busy night at Barnsley
OL,7,     FHopsital's casualty department, so
OL,8,     Fwhen Sister Benita arrives to head
OL,9,     Fthe shift, the corridors are
OL,10,     Falready packed full of patients.
OL,11,G2100 Ambulance: Code Red
OL,12,     FA crash leaves 29-year-old Ellie
OL,13,     Ftrapped in her car with critical
OL,14,     Finjuries. Meanwhile, 32-year-old
OL,15,     FClaire suffers a seizure at school
OL,16,     Fpickup, then seizes again en route
OL,17,     Fto hospital.
